item.title: About me
item.dc:creator: emerkelly
item.content:encoded:
I am a third year student in The Institute of Technology Blanchardstown, interested in Website and Graphic Design. Hoping to enter the field of Website Design upon graduation. I have a variety of skills that I have obtained during my studies such as PHP, Adobe Illustrator and Dreamweaver.
I am currently seeking work experience for early 2017.

item.content:encoded:

Parallax Website

This is a website that I worked on as part of my web design module in my second year of my degree. It is an interactive parallax website. The aim of the website is for children to learn about space while having a fun, interactive experience. I used dreamweaver to create the website along with illustrator and photoshop to create the characters Go to website
